00:25:28.770 --> 00:25:31.050
That's how you do it.

00:25:31.050 --> 00:25:32.465
You take each slice.

00:25:32.465 --> 00:25:33.840
You add the
cross-sectional area,

00:25:33.840 --> 00:25:36.170
and then you take a
little thickness, dy,

00:25:36.170 --> 00:25:38.330
and then you add all of them up.

00:25:38.330 --> 00:25:40.950
Because this is extending
over the whole plane,

00:25:40.950 --> 00:25:43.630
we're going to have to go all
the way from minus infinity

00:25:43.630 --> 00:25:45.100
to plus infinity.

00:25:45.100 --> 00:25:56.940
And this is the formula
for volumes by slicing.

00:25:56.940 --> 00:26:00.300
And now our goal, in order
