00:29:01.934 --> 00:29:04.350
Which is that this is the same
as e^(-b^2) times e^(-x^2).

00:29:07.120 --> 00:29:11.330
And that's going to be
the main way in which we

00:29:11.330 --> 00:29:15.590
use the particular function
that we're dealing with here.

00:29:15.590 --> 00:29:20.940
That's really the
